  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><em>You draw upon your arcane power to enhance your weapons with magical energy.</em><br /><br /><strong>Prerequisites</strong><br />Ability to cast arcane spells.<br /><br /><strong>Benefits</strong><br />As a swift action, you can imbue your weapons with a fraction of your power. For 1 round, your weapons deal +1 damage and are treated as magic for the purpose of overcoming damage reduction. For every five caster levels you possess, this bonus increases by +1, to a maximum of +5 at 20th level.<br /><br /><strong>Combat Trick</strong><br />You can spend any number of stamina points to increase the duration of this feat's effects by 1 round for each stamina point spent.</p>",
